Bob needs to install AGX using the Python that came with the Unified
Installer... So get into the directory where you untarred AGX and do:

/opt/plone/zeocluster/python/python setup.py install --no-compile

(I don't remember if that's the exact path to python, but you get the idea)

To use AGX you will need a script to make things easier. Put in the full
paths to the AGX command (which should end up in python/Scripts/), your
.xmi file, and the folder where you want your code to go. You can make a
script for each project you work on... Keep a link on your desktop and
you're set!

Have fun Bob,

